<div><h1>Product Safety</h1><p>All products sold by The Cream Cartel should be stored and used in accordance to the manufacturer's instructions located on product packaging.</p><p><br></p><p>Nitrous oxide (N2O) products by nature have the potential to be misused as a means to obtain a euphoric high by a user. Using nitrous oxide products for this purpose poses health risks and as a result The Cream Cartel implements a variety of measures in the sale of these products to help mitigate risks and harm associated with their sale.</p><p><br></p><p>For additional information and help regarding nitrous oxide please visit Hi-Ground at: <a href="https://hi-ground.org/">https://hi-ground.org/</a> </p></div>